{"word":"G1106 - γνώμη - gnṓmē - gno'-may - Advice","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">γνώμη</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">gnṓmē</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">gno'-may</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Advice</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"தீர்மானம், யோசனை, அபிப்பிராயம்,மனது - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"the faculty of knowing, mind, reasonl"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1097 - γινώσκω - ginṓskō - ghin-oce'-ko/1097\">G1097</a>; <i>cognition</i>, that is, (subjectively) <i>opinion</i>, or (objectively) <i>resolve</i> (<i>counsel</i>, <i>consent</i>, etc.): - advice, + agree, judgment, mind, purpose, will.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1097/1097\">G1097</a>, <a href=\"#/G1106/1106\">G1106</a>, <a href=\"#/G1107/1107\">G1107</a>, <a href=\"#/G1108/1108\">G1108</a>, <a href=\"#/G1110/1110\">G1110</a>, <a href=\"#/G176/176\">G176</a>, <a href=\"#/G1921/1921\">G1921</a>, <a href=\"#/G1922/1922\">G1922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2607/2607\">G2607</a>, <a href=\"#/G4267/4267\">G4267</a>, <a href=\"#/G4268/4268\">G4268</a>, <a href=\"#/G4774/4774\">G4774</a>"}]}